{"tid":2113464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓據報自研新冠病毒疫苗 專家質疑是否夠醫學水平","createTime":"2020-07-18T06:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T06:53:53.000Z","uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b86e90070097a746379a75f9a0079804eb693551","tid":2113464,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:46:52.000Z","msg":"北韓據報自研新冠病毒疫苗 專家質疑是否夠醫學水平<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538527-20200718.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538527-20200718.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiQX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=64c63ef2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538527-20200718.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7e43a201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538527-20200718.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f7ea0caff7618572ae10ad92dc705601c98c6658","tid":2113464,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:48:02.000Z","msg":"北韓據報正自行研發新型冠狀病毒疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社引述來自平壤的科研報告，指當地有醫學院轄下的醫學生物機構，領導疫苗研發工作，科學家今個月開始，進行動物試驗及臨床測試。報告說，已確定疫苗的免疫原性及安全性，正討論下階段臨床試驗。<br />\n<br />\n北韓至今未公布過任何新型肺炎確診個案。有專家質疑，以北韓的財政狀況與醫學水平，是否有能力研發疫苗。"},{"pid":"34b23eac02eb60f16cc62a83d396014e7da3a41d","tid":2113464,"uid":18477,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:48:22.000Z","msg":"something like this?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ez3fYLL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEz3fYLL.jpg&h=c84c055a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cd84e20ded4c304c5fc94883ecfcf25e38653a5","tid":2113464,"uid":363195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:50:01.000Z","msg":"邀請香港官員率先試吓"},{"pid":"be94c2131c2b2acdbc109d7c17f22ccab0a201e1","tid":2113464,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid